Amazon Virtual Private Cloud (VPC)

  Allows u to create a secure private network in the AWS.
  
  U are able to set up a private virtual network
  Isolate and protect resources

  Ex:
    launch resources like EC2 instances inside the VPC
    VPC spans AZs in a region



Network ACL 
  
  Access control lists (ACLs) ensure the proper traffic is allowed into the subnet.

Rourter and Route Table 
  
  Defines where netword traffic is routed

Internet Gateway

  Allows public traffic to the internet through the VCP

VPC peering allows you to connect 2 VPCs toguether 
  Peering facilitates the transfer of data in a secure manner.


